highlights.text: “Jingle Bell Rock - Daryl's Version” by Daryl Hall & John Oates is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 123 spots at #71.
Ariana Grande has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Santa Tell Me” is the highest at #3.
“Christmas Without You” by Ava Max is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #102.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 203 weeks straight.
